esponding ""too busy right now to answer"" on this, or that I am not *required* to play nicely here makes this experiment invalid, so let me know what that means in your case. And with that, I'll copy your letter on to this Word Trigger thread. Added: /me wonders, was it just 47, as per Nyquist, that wanted to warn you about your surroundings? because this has become apparently necessary: that I once made the wink implied by sqr, too square, a wish;",14.533499977099728,11.867836020464441
