Belinda made 230 flyers to distribute around town with the help of her friends. Ryan passed out 1/6 of the flyers, Alyssa passed out 2/5, Scott passed out 3/10, and Belinda passed out the rest. What percentage of the flyers did Belinda pass out?
Ryan passed out 230*1/6 = 38.333 flyers.
Alyssa passed out 230*2/5 = 92 flyers.
Scott passed out 230*3/10 = 69 flyers.
So, Ryan, Alyssa, and Scott passed out 38.333+92+69 = 200.333 flyers altogether.
Belinda passed out the rest, which is 230-200.333 = 29.667 flyers.
The percentage of the flyers Belinda passed out is (29.667/230)*100 = 12.86%.
